<plot>Joe and James are bored newspapermen who stumble across a bright paralegal in distress who had found out that her prominent attorney boss is a protector of the manatee because he is harvesting them to use them as aphrodisiacs to sell to Asian buyers online. Southwest Florida scenic conspiracy thriller is a story about love, friendship, taking risks and taking a stand. Manatee protection has a wicked and devious motive when the protectors are actually killing, harvesting and selling ground up manatee parts as a competitor to Viagra illegally online as part of a Columbian mafia effort in Fort Myers, Florida.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?009474</url></doc>
